<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَمِنْهَا:</span> <span style="color:#008000">(لَوْمَا)</span> فِي قَوْلِكَ: <span style="color:#008000">(لَوْمَا عَمْرٌو لأَكْرَمْتُكَ)</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَمِنْهَا:</span> <span style="color:#008000">(أَمَّا)</span> فِي قَوْلِكَ: <span style="color:#008000">(أَمَّا زَيْدٌ فَقَدْ ذَهَبَ)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَمِنْهَا:</span> <span style="color:#008000">(عَسَى)</span> فِي قَوْلِكَ: <span style="color:#008000">(عَسَى زَيْدٌ يَذْهَبُ)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَمِنْهَا:</span> <span style="color:#008000">(إِنْ)</span> فِي قَوْلِكَ: <span style="color:#008000">(إِنْ زَيْدٌ إِلَّا قَائِمٌ)</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَمِثْلُ ذَلِكَ:</span> الأَدَوَاتُ الأُخْرَى الَّتِي ذَكَرَهَا المُصَنِّفُ؛ فَأَكْثَرُ مَا يَأْتِي بَعْدَهَا مَرْفُوعٌ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>